videos.description: Zion Williamson drives to the rim and bulldozes Derrick Favors out of the way while getting a layup to go.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion proves to be too much for Favors) 2021/01/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion proves to be too much for Favors

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell flies to the basket and at the last moment, lasers a pass out to Bojan Bogdanovic for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell slings dime to Bogdanovic for 3-pointer) 2021/01/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell slings dime to Bogdanovic for 3-pointer

videos.description: Zion tries to go coast-to-coast for a basket, but Rudy Gobert meets him at the rim for a block.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert denies Zion at the rim) 2021/01/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert denies Zion at the rim

videos.description: Zion Williamson steals the ball from Donovan Mitchell and then breaks away for a layup.
